{"type":null,"faqId":44581,"title":"亲情关怀是什么？能够解决哪些问题？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.25in;margin-left:1.0381944in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.19791667in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>亲情关怀是一款支持手机远程协助的应用，只需在手机上轻轻一点，就可以远程求助他人、或者远程帮助他人解决手机问题。就像操作自己的手机一样简单方便。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>支持向本地联系人发起求助</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>远程查看和控制对方手机</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>远程帮助对方修改手机设置、下载安装应用程序等操作</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>远程在对方手机上涂鸦，直观指引操作</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5.  </span><span>支持语音通话，沟通更高效</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>华为手机中已经预装了亲情关怀，可从桌面打开“手机服务”，点击“远程协助”直接使用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"82","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400981000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":11,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"亲情关怀,解决","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}